### Manual Verification Path
To manually trigger a reconciliation run:
```bash
curl -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <CRON_SECRET>" \
  https://your-domain.com/api/cron/reconcile-payments
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Ensure the `CRON_SECRET`, `PAYMOB_API_KEY`, and `FINANCE_ADMIN_EMAIL` environment variables are correctly configured in your deployment environment.
